"...Ah" [l][r]
[r]While out shopping at night, it suddenly started raining and I ran into a convenience store to escape. I took out my smartphone to check a notification I had forgotten. [l][r]
On the screen was a call history from a person I hadn't heard from in a long time.[l][r]
[r] In order not to get in the way of the people who had also come to escape the rain, I left the shop and moved to a shady area where the rain was not hitting me. [l][r]
Then I selected one call and pressed the call button. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

