"Think carefully" [r]
"Kanazawa said. [l]I answered as few words as possible so that he wouldn't know what was going on in my mind, and then I ended the call. [l][r]
[r]I rushed back to my room after doing the bare minimum of shopping, but I couldn't even bring myself to put the things I bought in the fridge. [l][r]

[r]Well, you have to think about it carefully. [l][r]
