Kanazawa carefully chose his words and explained to me what I wanted to know to the best of his ability.[l][r]

[r]"Honestly, I never thought we'd find that vehicle again. But then I got an anonymous email. I never found out who it was from..." [l][r]
According to the investigation report, the Kettenkrad, with its unknown owner, is indeed located exactly where the email stated."[l][r]
[r]It seems Kanazawa hasn't actually seen it yet either[r]
He said that his wife had given birth to a baby, but her body was not stable, so he couldn't go and check on her directly. [l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

