But now that she knows the baby is growing well and she can give birth without worry, she plans to go and check it out soon, Kanazawa said apologetically.[l][r]
[r]When I said congratulations, Kanazawa was quietly pleased. I was also somehow happy. But that was where the story began. [l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

