"To be honest, I think it's a little dangerous.
Ugh. What if Chito touches that vehicle again and falls down? [l][r]
And now you're here. I have no idea what the outcome will be.'[l][r]

[r]Of course, scientifically speaking, there is no way that a mere military vehicle could have such mysterious powers. [l][r]
But we've already had experiences that go beyond normal common sense.[l][r]
So I thought Kanazawa's concerns were valid.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

