[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[cm]That girl who took us everywhere. [l][r]
The vehicle that could run anywhere with its small tires and heavy tracks. [l][r]
If it was just Chi-chan, I could only take her heart. But now I'm here too. So... [l][r]
[r]No matter how absurd the idea is, or how small the hope, I think Chi-chan right now would want to try it. [l][r]
[r] Kanazawa said that I should decide whether to tell him or not. He also consulted with Ishii, but they decided that it was better for me to make the decision. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

