[r] (Isn't it a matter of which? Ishii and Kanazawa are strangers after all. It's irresponsible.) [l][r]

[r]That's true. But it's kind of you. You could have kept quiet forever, but you told me because you thought it might help Chi-chan cheer up. [l][r]
[r] (It was just a burden to keep hiding it. That's just an excuse for indecision.) [l][r]

