(... Yeah. Well, I guess so.) [l][r]
[r]That's what it was. If it's ultimately up to me to decide, then I should decide whether to tell Chi-chan or not. [l][r]
As expected, neither Kanazawa nor Ishii lived long enough to waste their time. They thought things through well. That's great. [l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

