(... What on earth has happened to you all of a sudden, Yuri? ... You're like...) [l][r]
"...Thank you." [l][r]
[r] I said out loud to the me in the mirror who was looking at me curiously.
[l]In the mirror, I looked a little surprised and my eyes widened. [l][r]
[r] "...you...?" [l][r]

I heard Chi-chan's voice. A voice searching for me. "Chi-chan, I'm okay," I replied, leaving the sink and entering the room where Chi-chan was. [l][r]
